Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't even touch him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll take away our soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now... I can't beat this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I would have completely lost in that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take away your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Photon Steam of-!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Duel is interrupted!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that Duel wasn't interrupted... I would've been annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're always around me that why my soul was targeted...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what are you whining about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to survive is to defeat Kaito, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.60,0:01:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's not "can we win", it's "we will win"!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't only your problem anymore-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotori... Tetsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Duel Carnival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, W.D.C. for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it will be held in our Heartland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievably strong Duelists from all over the world are gathered for this carnival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That means him too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yuma, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I have to send you on a small errand!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.92,0:02:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.71,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not free right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where my {\i1}adorable, obedient{\i0} grandson went to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here! You're obedient grandson is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the heck is this a "small errand", Grandma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like you, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you drop your "bringing it to em'" attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!? If I don't have what it takes to bring it to em', then what do I have left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'LL BRING IT TO EM'!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an untidy place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monkey, a monkey, a MONKEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, Right here, here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no monkey. It's an old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're all ingredients to color each day. \NDon't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, I was lonely. Until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lied to myself that being alone was easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite books and hobbies,\N they don't seem to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were the only one to nod in agreement with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happiness and sadness and anger and\N Do and Re and Mi and Fa and So and La and Ti and Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't work unless they're different,\N the harmony and the scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one is exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because that's the reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the sounds are dissonant from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't give up on the strength that will get you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we reach the edge of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the view we see will be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all ingredients to color each day.\N Don't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious, Kotori-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(236,487.5)}Numbers 15
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(788,571.5)}A Fight to the Death, The Duel Lodge: A Legendary Monster is Reborn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little longer and I was going to starve!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank Haru-{\i1}san{\i0} very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-{\i1}san{\i0} huh, What does my Grandma have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I receive a lot of assistance from your caring grandma, Haru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I'm the master of this Duel Lodge... Rokujuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Lodge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let Yuma go to the Duel Lodge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it would be dangerous for Yuma to Duel anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still too young...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he can find his real purpose in Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. There's no path now, and besides until the day comes, your hearts are just too thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you guys can sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who works eats, no, maybe you should sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tetsuo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, please put that over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, you shouldn't be slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do the cleaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of the old man, he went to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes, Neos...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary monsters are all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Yuma don't slack off-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those statues are Duel Monsters that I put my soul into making!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to rise disciples, I had to make statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciples?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel Lodge is a place to train Duelist to be winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many formed Duelist were raised right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These Monster statues look as if they're about to move
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The statues can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, certainly in a Duel that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to contribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On both of our fields, the legendary stones have already been summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have The Blue-Eyes Statue Dragon, and The Red-Eyes Statue Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you have Statue Black Magician, and Statue Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The decks we're using are the stone decks used in the Duel Lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our legendary stone monsters are all statues right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their powers have been sealed and their attack power are 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? So they can't move after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may move, they may not. It all depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depends on Yuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, the duel is all relying on the player's strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, the monsters on the field have an effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the keys to your cards are within the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing? You have the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Field Magic, B2 Zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Field Magic, B2 Zone, is a card that releases the statue monsters from their effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move now, monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to awaken the Legendary Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, The Red-Eyes and The Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Go, Black Magician, attack Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too shabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is entertaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, did you really make the monsters move just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bla-Magi just destroyed Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true duel begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Bla--Magi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become the monster!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've become the monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send the 3 Blue-Eyes from my field and hand to the cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuse now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Fusion Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Ultimate Statue Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Dragon attacks Bla-Magi Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Burst!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bla-Magi Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from my hand I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Fusion Cancel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fusion Monster returns to my extra deck, and I Special Summon the Fusion Material Monsters from my cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be Reborn! The 3 Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Facing this fear, anybody would be terrified. That's a natural thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster's are always exposed to this fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! The 3 Blue-Eyes attack Bla-Magi no.. Yuma directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit too harsh there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sensed the monster's fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you understood what they Monsters were feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you know the Monsters thoughts, they'll answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those thoughts made the monsters awaken from death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I know their thoughts, they'll answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even monsters sense fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they can overcome it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yuma! How long do you plan on staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go back just go, I'll stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll prepare the breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did such a horrible thing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't it be repaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy truly has some character.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A shining character
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've returned, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamakiwa, You've become unconscious because of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to drag you down...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:16:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a sec, who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is this guy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my former disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must you insist on seeking the darkness!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light is what makes you strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see that you're destroying yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... Be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time I'll defeat you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the Hidden Deck within the Duel Lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the Hidden Deck within the Duel Lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'll hand it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish one, who's heart is concurred by darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll cut all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you? And why are you interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm... I'm the old man's disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A disciple of that lousy old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone that disrespects my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting, I'll drag you into the darkness too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel-Disk set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, I'll fight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you feeling down, just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was taught something at this lodge too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm a disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the first move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I set 1 card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn... Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Armored Ninja Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then from my hand I activate the Magic Card, Armored Ninjutsu: Quick Teleport!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, I can Special Summon a monster whose attack power is less than Armored Ninja Flame's!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, Armored Ninja Air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Quick Teleport's effect, Flame and Air can't attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two level 4 monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay the level 4 Armored Ninja Flame and Armored Ninja Air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two monsters will construct the overlay network!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, Armored Ninja Blade Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already summoned a Xyz Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This speed isn't just normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Ninja Blade Heart attacks Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap open! Gagaga Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card becomes an equip card to a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip it to Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slice him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sudden Rapid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Strike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Shield, it protects Gagaga Magician from destruction for 2 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you'll still take the damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Armored Ninja Blade Heart, once per turn by detaching one overlay unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can attack a monster once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the damage once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, even if you protect the monster you'll still take the damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:22:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are fighting to overcome their fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll protect my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, you say? What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut those thoughts and your monsters and crush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's this week's quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the start of the Duel, how many cards are in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4, 5, or maybe 6?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's test is hard. I can't divide myself from pleasure and temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna watch TV when I get home.\N The recent anime are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, this test is hard. \NLanguage, Math and English are especially bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm only average at science and social studies.\N The only thing I'm good at is P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Wait up, Baby!) For who's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Is that, Baby!) ...am I remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Just hold on, Baby!) ...the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(What are we!? Baby!) ...they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I write the correct answer on this paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one year, in ten years, will anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world I drew in the corner of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}one day I will race through the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can blame this heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing is really correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamikawa, the old man's previous disciple...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His skillful Ninja Deck has me cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:24:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who aims for victory, even at the sacrifice of his own Monsters... is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel's kinda scary for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! My Monster's are my friends, the ones I fight alongside!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in those friends and protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll fight alongside them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Deadliest Ninja Arts! The Most Terrifying Ninja!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer's five!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You draw the first five cards off the top of your deck into your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Duel starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.90,0:24:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get to it, don't go forgetting to draw a card!
